								A neat visual representation of osu! stats aswell as an in depth
								analysis of information such as rankings, top play data,
								and top ranked players
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>


				<div class="col l3 m4 s12">
					<div class="card" style="border-radius: 6px;">
						<div class="card-header" style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.4em;" data-redirect="stats">
							<h5>
								Stats
							</h5>
						</div>
						<div class="card-content" style="text-align: center;">
