							<h5>
								Recommendation App
							</h5>
						</div>
						<div class="card-content" style="text-align: center;">
							<p>
								osu! recommendation application, this will function with all osu! game modes. After provided
								an inputed username the app takes in certain user data points
								(skill group, maps played, maps preformed well on, time played, rank, etc) and
								returns a set of maps that the user most likey will perform well on performance wise
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
